  "description": "This individual presents the desiccated anatomy of the long-dead, with light skin drawn tight over a sharply defined skull and tendon-bound jaw. Gray eyes sit deep in hollow sockets, unblinking and fixed, while black hair persists in sparse, brittle lengths clinging to the scalp. The frame is gaunt and upright, its hands elongated and knotted, bearing the rigid articulation typical of reanimated remains. Dentition shows through receded lips, and the overall visage is cadaverous and unmistakably undead.",
